{
  "chapter": 51,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙夜访朱姬，得知储君被赵穆用药物控制且守卫森严，营救难度极大。朱姬突然透露被软禁的孩子并非她的亲生儿子。赵穆突然来访，项少龙藏入床下暗格，偷听到赵穆已控制赵雅、密谋对付乌家。项少龙脱身后找到赵倩，确认赵倩未将纪嫣然救他们的事泄露给赵雅，但得知赵雅确已背叛。赵倩讲述奶娘因骂赵穆被赐死的往事，坚定随项少龙出逃的决心。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙吗？快进来！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙！我可以信任你吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "看来夫人没有可以选择的余地了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "就算我可以信任你，你又凭什么本事把我们母子带出去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "这正是我来找夫人商量的原因，因为我猜到赵穆必会把所有人手集中在储君处。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你非常精明，难怪赵穆这么忌惮你。每次他们说到你时，我都很留心在听，没想到不韦竟找到你，真的很好。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "储君那里的情况如何？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "除非你率领大军，攻破邯郸城，否则休想把他带走。自异人郎君登基后，赵穆调来二百名身手高强的武士，日夜不停轮班在大宅内陪守他，外面则加建高墙，形成宅内有宅，且长期有一营近千人的禁卫军在守卫着，若非你能化作鸟儿，休想潜进去见他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "而且就算把他救出去也没用，赵穆乃用药的大行家，给他喂服一种奇异的药物，必须定期服用解药才可没事，若没解药吃，不出十天立便要毒发身亡。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "这样扣着储君，除了用为出气外，对赵人有什么好处？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你也应听过赵穆的阴谋，故意以酒色把他变成废人，说真的，赵穆恨不得把他送回去当秦王。现在却不是时候，因为会便宜了吕不韦，你明白吗？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这小子死了倒好，见到他我便无名火起。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "来！到榻上再说。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "恐怕时地都不适合吧！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你以为人家不知道吗？只不过那些婢女奉命每隔一段时间便来看我，躲在榻上，安全得多了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "奴家要告诉你一个天大的秘密，但要你先发毒誓，不可以告诉任何人，方可以让你知道。唉！我亦是别无选择，不得不告诉你。我在这里不准踏出屋门半步，又没有任何可信任的人。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我项少龙一言九鼎，答应人的话，绝不食言，夫人放心好了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我知你是言必有信的人，可是奴家仍不放心，你便当迁就人家吧！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他们软禁的那孩子根本不是我的儿子。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bi_nv",
      "speaker_name": "婢女",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "夫人睡了吗？侯爷来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "美人儿，本侯来探望你了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "侯爷今天精神焕发，定是发生令你高兴的事，奴家很替你开心呢！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "听说你的吕郎派了图先到邯郸来救你，美人儿你高兴吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "你还不知奴家的心意吗？没有了你，什么地方人家也不想去，而且这只是谣言罢了！谁会蠢得到这里来送死？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "怎会是谣言？现在秦国旧臣正与吕不韦展开激烈斗争，要他负上毒杀先王的责任，恐怕连你的庄襄王都护不了他。吕不韦死了，我自会把你们母子送回咸阳，那时可不要把我忘记。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "不回去！不回去！人家绝不回去，由政儿回去好了，我要留在这里和你长相厮守。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "我今天这么开心，是因为赵雅那贱人终于落到我算计里，难以自拔。没有人比我更清楚她，既迷恋荣华富贵，又贪新忘旧，不过她对项少龙已是很特别的了。幸好我还有一招杀手锏，就是教孝成王动以兄妹之情，加上利害关系，哪到她不诚心就范！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "为何你整天咬牙切齿提着那项少龙，他和奴家有什么关系？人家对他一点兴趣都没有。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "怎会没有关系，乌家一直和吕不韦有联络，项少龙是乌家的孙婿，吕不韦若来偷人，自须借助乌家的力量。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "项少龙莫落到我手里，那时我会令他后悔做人。我操他时，你得在旁看热闹。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "那个毛头小子怎斗得过你呢？他迟早总会落到你手里，任你施为。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "来！上榻吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_ji",
      "speaker_name": "朱姬",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "我看项少龙定是不折不扣的蠢材，否则怎会相信以淫荡闻名天下的赵雅会对他专心一意？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "你错哩！赵雅对项少龙确是动了真情，所以很多事直到此刻仍替他隐瞒。不过我太明白她了，所以她怎斗得过我，她不想和项少龙一块儿死，只好乖乖与我合作。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_zhu_ji",
      "text": "项少龙这小子不但不蠢，还非常厉害，若不是抓着赵雅这弱点，鹿死谁手，尚未可知呢。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谢天谢地",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "倩儿！是少龙！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "你有没有把嫣然救我们的事告诉雅夫人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "她不是有什么不妥吧？为何说给她听会有问题？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "那是说你已告诉她了！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "没有。但并非我不信任她，而是我曾答应嫣然姊，绝不把这事告诉任何人，所以只把我们编好的故事告诉她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "天啊！夫人究竟做了什么事，要劳你半夜三更偷进来问倩儿这样的问题？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "今晚你有没有见过她呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听说她有客人来了，所以我不方便过去。噢！我想起来哩！每次说有客人来，小昭她们的神情都很古怪，似乎充满怨愤，又无法作声的样子，那客人难道是……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎啊！求你告诉人家是什么一回事好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "这几天你觉得夫人有什么异样的地方吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "给你这样一说，夫人果然似和以前不同，不时心神恍惚，有次我还发觉她独自一人在垂泪，问起她时，她只说想起妮夫人，有时又无端端发下人的脾气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "究竟是什么一回事啊！人家的心憋得很难受呢！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "你再想想，她有没有说过什么特别的话，例如我们绝逃不出去诸如此类的话。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这倒没有，但她曾提过吕不韦现在自身难保，随时有抄家灭族的大祸，我们若随乌家去投靠他，等若由狼口走进虎口里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "那你怎样答她？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我说只要能跟着你，死也没关系。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是了！当时她神情很古怪，回想起来，似乎像既羞惭又后悔的样子，后来便借故走了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "你至紧要表现得若无其事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "倩儿晓得了，我对你这新圣人有无比的信心，知你定能领着倩儿和乌家安然度过劫难。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_qian",
      "text": "你真舍得丢下父王，随我去接受茫不可测的命运吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_qian",
      "speaker_name": "赵倩",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "只要能离开父王，倩儿什么都不怕。人家有件事尚未告诉你，就是娘死后，倩儿的奶娘曾说了句骂赵穆的话，辗转传到父王那里，他便立即赐奶娘毒酒，奶娘临死前握着我的手垂泪叮嘱，若有机会定要远离王宫，做个平常人家的女儿比做公主强多了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 51,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    }
